{"about_the_game":"Trawel is a historically-inaccurate <strong>open world text adventure RPG</strong>. Created as a re-imagining of old-school calculator and early command line games, it eschews their limitations but attempts to capture their spirit, and bring it in line with modern quality of life standards with a graphical GUI.<br><br>Oldschool games often were limited by memory, processing power, displays, and inputs. Trawel is heavily data-driven, with partly-procedural, partly-handcrafted abstract environments. Visuals are used as aides, and do not determine the gameplay.<br><br>Of particular note, the Graphical version here offers a mouse/controller/keyboard interface to make playing the game easier for those used to modern applications.<br>The game will also boot in text-only mode at the same time, which tends to be compatible with most screen readers.<br><br>Trawel gameplay is heavily focused on exploring the world, finding better gear, and deciding to use it or sell it. It also features an opportunistic choice-oriented combat system.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The bigger they are...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/992240/05edf70a9e575c516ad1cb5d0571b9b489216ce6.jpg"},{"name":"...the harder they fall.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/992240/990897760805c3323a680676d6960a9ae4697259.jpg"},{"name":"Landed: Lot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/992240/881d469279fff29b4779ab22b9db888543a628b8.jpg"},{"name":"Service: Relaxation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/992240/ab72a923d159347233852462f62e4a3751781f65.jpg"},{"name":"Veneration: Adopted","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/992240/6d099d21c7f501775527ec879a3c3ab2d0ddd3d6.jpg"},{"name":"Half Dead, All Alive","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/a